text:
Rohanpur A.b. Govt. High School also known as Rohanpur Ahmadi Begum Government High School is an school in Gomastapur, Chapai Nawabganj.
History.
It was established on 1939 under Maldah Education board in Bangabari Union as Minor English school or M.E School.
Education system.
It's now under the Rajshahi Education Board. The institute has following Science, Business Studies, Humanities disciplines.
